1 Bari; Cagliari 0-4 Udinese; Catania 1-0 Sampdoria; Chievo 0-1
Fiorentina; Genoa 1-0 Palermo; Lecce 0-1 Bologna; Roma 2-0
Lazio; Parma 1-3 Napoli.  Spain: Almeria 2-2 Atletico Madrid; Real  Madrid  2-0 Hercules;
Real Zaragoza 4-0 Valencia; Espanyol 2-0 Deportivo La Coruna;
Osasuna 3-1 Racing Santander; Real Sociedad 0-2 Malaga; Levante
1-1 Real Mallorca; Villarreal 1-1 Sporting Gijon; Sevilla 1-1
Barcelona. Today: Getafe v Athletic Bilbao.    Germany : Cologne 4-0 Hanover; Wolfsburg 1-2 Nuremberg; Bayern
Munich 6-0 Hamburg; Schalke 2-1 Eintracht Frankfurt; Hoffenheim
1-0 Borussia Dortmund; Kaiserslautern 2-1 Freiburg; Werder
Bremen 1-1 Borussia Moenchengladbach; Mainz 0-1 Bayer
Leverkusen; St. Pauli 1-2 Stuttgart.  France: Rennes 0-2 Marseille; Nancy 2-0 Caen; Nice 1-0 Auxerre;
